        "body": "### What does this PR do?\r\nPrevents JavaScript runtime errors when the shortcuts toggle checkbox or\r\nshortcuts dialog elements are not present on the page.\r\n\r\n### Why?\r\nSome admin pages do not render these elements, which previously caused\r\nerrors when initializing keyboard shortcuts.\r\n\r\n### Changes\r\n- Added null checks for toggle checkbox and dialog\r\n- Ensured shortcuts still initialize correctly when toggle is missing\r\n\r\n### Tests\r\n- Existing test suite passes\r\n- This issue came up while testing admin pages that do not include the\r\nshortcuts toggle.\r\n",
